00:44:25.090 --> 00:44:28.520
Well, I'm going to read
one that's kind of, maybe,

00:44:28.520 --> 00:44:32.700
I don't know if it will work today.

00:44:32.700 --> 00:44:37.400
But Carver was a very
deeply religious person.

00:44:37.400 --> 00:44:44.690
He taught a Bible class once a week
at Tuskegee for the entire duration

00:44:44.690 --> 00:44:49.640
of his teaching at Tuskegee
which was almost 50 years.

00:44:49.640 --> 00:44:54.200
He -- the -- the Bible study
class started in a small classroom

00:44:54.200 --> 00:44:58.670
and within a few years, it was in
the largest lecture hall on campus.

00:44:58.670 --> 00:45:00.630
It lasted about 15 minutes.

00:45:00.630 --> 00:45:03.580
There are a couple
of collections of --

00:45:03.580 --> 00:45:06.820
of Carver's teachings
remembered by students.

00:45:06.820 --> 00:45:11.250
And this is one of his --
one of Carver's teachings,

00:45:11.250 --> 00:45:16.040
which may be relevant
to the events in Orlando

00:45:16.040 --> 00:45:19.710
and to the horrible police murders.

00:45:19.710 --> 00:45:24.770
This is how Carver taught
people to deal with them.

00:45:24.770 --> 00:45:27.090
The poem is called, "Goliath."

00:45:27.090 --> 00:45:30.890
And it's -- it's about a
period when there were a lot

00:45:30.890 --> 00:45:33.920
of lynchings in the south.

00:45:33.920 --> 00:45:35.870
Another lynching.

00:45:35.870 --> 00:45:38.570
Madness grips the south.

00:45:38.570 --> 00:45:44.630
A black man's hacked off penis in
his mouth, his broken body torched.

00:45:44.630 --> 00:45:50.780
The terrorized blacks cower
and the whites are satanized.

00:45:50.780 --> 00:45:56.310
His students ask in Carver's
Bible class, where is God now?

00:45:56.310 --> 00:45:59.870
What does he want from us?

00:45:59.870 --> 00:46:02.790
Professor Carver smiles.

00:46:02.790 --> 00:46:06.100
God is right here.

00:46:06.100 --> 00:46:09.320
Don't lose contact with him.

00:46:09.320 --> 00:46:12.190
Don't yield to fear.

00:46:12.190 --> 00:46:19.160
Fear is the root of hate
and hate destroys the hater.

00:46:19.160 --> 00:46:22.540
When Saul's army went to
war against the Philistines,

00:46:22.540 --> 00:46:29.160
the Israelites lost contact,
fearful of Goliath's might.

00:46:29.160 --> 00:46:36.690
When we lose contact, we see
only hate, only injustice,

00:46:36.690 --> 00:46:41.830
a giant so great it's
shadow blocks our son.

00:46:41.830 --> 00:46:46.760
But David slew Goliath with
the only things he knew,

00:46:46.760 --> 00:46:52.330
the slingshot of intelligence
and one pebble

00:46:52.330 --> 00:46:57.060
of truth, and the battle was done.

00:46:57.060 --> 00:47:03.940
We kill Goliath by going about
the business of the universal good

00:47:03.940 --> 00:47:10.420
which our Creator wills, obediently
yielding to Him the opportunity

00:47:10.420 --> 00:47:15.740
to work wonders through us
for all of His children.

00:47:15.740 --> 00:47:17.270
That's all.

00:47:17.270 --> 00:47:21.890
Read 1 Samuel 17:47.

00:47:21.890 --> 00:47:24.510
