00:56:58.070 --> 00:57:01.460
I get out, I go to Baruch College.

00:57:01.460 --> 00:57:04.980
And just as, you know, the
stars align and destiny

00:57:04.980 --> 00:57:08.230
and all this stuff, I happen to
take a black literature course

00:57:08.230 --> 00:57:14.750
by Addison Gayle, Jr., the chief
proponent of The Black Aesthetic.

00:57:14.750 --> 00:57:18.810
I didn't know that at the time,
of course, but he used to --

00:57:18.810 --> 00:57:20.640
he used to hold court
in the classroom

00:57:20.640 --> 00:57:25.000
