01:00:55.990 --> 01:01:01.560
My -- and -- and I was encouraged
by my family, the -- my --

01:01:01.560 --> 01:01:05.340
my father was interested
in poetry and wrote.

01:01:05.340 --> 01:01:12.060
And then, in our -- although
there were no collections of --

01:01:12.060 --> 01:01:17.070
then it as negro -- poetry
in the school libraries

01:01:17.070 --> 01:01:19.840
or public libraries
wherever we were,

01:01:19.840 --> 01:01:23.470
